## Usage Examples

### File Change Detection
```javascript
// When editing src/utils/calculator.js
// Automatically runs:
// - src/utils/__tests__/calculator.test.js
// - src/components/__tests__/Calculator.test.js
// - Any integration tests using calculator

const changedFiles = ['src/utils/calculator.js'];
const affectedTests = testRunner.getAffectedTests(changedFiles);
// Returns: [
//   'src/utils/__tests__/calculator.test.js',
//   'src/components/__tests__/Calculator.test.js'
// ]
```

